## 4. Unified Strategy: GIGASHIELD NEXUS ENTERPRISE

### Core Philosophy
> *"The precision of a startup. The architecture of an enterprise. The heart of India's workers."*

We take **info2's enterprise architecture and innovation** and merge it with **info1's execution discipline and demo simplicity**, while adding **novel differentiators** that neither file addresses.

### What We KEEP from info1
- ✅ 3-tier weekly pricing model (simple, constraint-aligned)
- ✅ 5 parametric trigger types with concrete thresholds
- ✅ Razorpay sandbox instant payout demo
- ✅ Clean 5-minute demo flow structure
- ✅ < 60 sec onboarding target
- ✅ Quick-commerce persona focus

### What We KEEP from info2
- ✅ Guidewire Cloud Platform integration (APD, PolicyCenter, ClaimCenter)
- ✅ Shield-SAC pricing engine (simplified for demo — pre-trained weights, not real-time training)
- ✅ PADS fraud detection (basic IMU validation for MVP, not full kinematic chain)
- ✅ XAI dashboard (SHAP values for premium transparency)
- ✅ Zero-touch claims via Analytics Manager + App Events
- ✅ Emotional demo script (Rahul's story)
- ✅ Bima Sugam compliance positioning
- ✅ Competitive matrix narrative

### What We ADD (New Differentiators)
- 🆕 **WhatsApp-first onboarding**: Worker signs up via WhatsApp bot in Hindi/Marathi/Tamil — no app download needed
- 🆕 **Shield Pools**: Micro community insurance pools — workers in same zone share risk, reducing individual premiums by 15-20%
- 🆕 **Disruption Severity Index (DSI)**: Composite score combining weather + traffic + platform order volume to create hyperlocal disruption severity — not just binary triggers
- 🆕 **ROI Calculator**: Real-time dashboard showing premium-vs-expected-loss ratio for each worker — transparency as a feature
- 🆕 **Regulatory Compliance Layer**: IRDAI sandbox alignment + PMJJBY mapping + Bima Sugam readiness

### What We CUT (De-risking)
- ❌ ConvLSTM training (use pre-trained weather models + heuristics; mention ConvLSTM as v2 roadmap)
- ❌ GNN fraud rings (mention as future capability, not demo)
- ❌ Self-healing Kubernetes (use standard autoscaling; mention predictive scaling as roadmap)
- ❌ Jutro Design Tokens (use React + Tailwind for speed)
- ❌ Full PADS kinematic chain (basic IMU spoofing detection only for demo)

