## 6. Risk Mitigation Matrix

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Shield-SAC fails to converge | Medium | High | Pre-train on synthetic data; fallback to gradient-boosted model with fairness post-processing |
| PADS IMU integration complex | Medium | Medium | Mock IMU data for demo; show architecture diagram for real implementation |
| Guidewire Cloud access issues | Low | Critical | Prepare mock Guidewire screens + API simulations; architecture diagrams still score points |
| Demo breaks during presentation | Medium | Critical | Record backup demo video; have 2 independent demo paths |
| Time overrun on ML components | High | High | ML is pre-trained weights + inference API only; no training during hackathon |

